ment, subpar. (B) read as follows: “the Secretary designates as a covered printed circuit board, after reasonable notice, based on a determination that the designation is required to support national security.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(4) to (6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/81/s851/a/2/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–81, § 851(a)(2)(B)","children":[],"tail":", added pars. (4) to (6)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/81/s851/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–81, § 851(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", amended subsec. (d) generally. Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “Not later than "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-05-01"},"text":"May 1, 2022","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary shall promulgate regulations, after an opportunity for notice and comment, implementing this section.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idaaa9ee73-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idaaa9ee74-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2021 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/81/s1701/e/1/A"},"text":"section 1701(e)(1)(A) of Pub. L. 117–81","children":[],"tail":", renumbering "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2358d"},"text":"section 2358d of this title","children":[],"tail":" as this section, deemed to have taken effect immediately before "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/s1881"},"text":"section 1881 of Pub. L. 116–283","children